The tag submit/review/ryan_ware/8253/20130814.161953 was pushed, but it was not completed because of the following reason(s):

- The date ryan_ware/8253/20130814.161953 in tag does NOT follow correct format. You can use shell command "date --utc +%Y%m%d.%H%M%S" to generate it, like 20120801.083113.
- The tag means you want to submit commit d5a874a313396f47c71b822a4eb270c3ea6b337c in review branch to OBS, but this commit does NOT exist in review branch. Please use correct branch name as version in tag name submit/{version}/{date.time}.
